# Assets Gross Of Provisions Excluding Derivatives Amount

## identifier
de8215

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of assets, gross of provisions for impairment, and excluding derivative financial instruments.

The measurement and classification basis used for assets is to be determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.GrossOfProvisionsExcludingDerivatives.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
